headline: Health Net Providing Special Assistance to Members Affected by Bird Flu Throughout California
summary: In response to Gov. Gavin Newsom's declared state of emergency in California, Health Net, one of the state's most experienced Medi-Cal managed care health plans and company of Centene Corporation (NYSE: CNC), is providing special assistance to members affected by the Bird Flu. Health Net is committed to ensuring its members have uninterrupted access to essential prescription medications, critical Health Net information and healthcare services.
